{"tid":1800772,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連登第一屆足球 Team of Decade 選舉正式開始","createTime":"2019-12-28T06:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T05:15:51.000Z","uid":318684,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8590943bd7e1c2c3ac99ec82c590976606321a","tid":1800772,"uid":318684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"平心而論，2010-2019　Team of Decade　會有邊o的人？<br />\n<br />\n小弟睇波年資尚淺，認為以下球員值得入選。<br />\n<br />\n註：本屆選舉所採用的陣形為傳統433　及　括號內為後備之人選<br />\n<br />\n門將：紐亞（聖卡斯）<br />\n左閘：馬細路（艾巴）<br />\n中堅：堤阿高施華、基亞連尼<br />\n右閘：艾維斯（拿姆）<br />\n防中：布斯基斯（小豬）<br />\n中場：恩尼斯達、大衛施華<br />\n左翼：c朗（列貝利）<br />\n前鋒：利雲度夫斯基（咬人蘇）<br />\n右翼：美斯（洛賓）<br />\n<br />\n小弟真係年資好淺，大家有任何意見就發表一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0c6ff20f724b4bc9fb30cf99414be2e8a24fa8","tid":1800772,"uid":34293,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"2019利記"},{"pid":"2ba0f9970f2b1bd527506f4823f8e491144fc6a1","tid":1800772,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"拉狗屌打施華"},{"pid":"9e8a1b3f26fce57341071088b72d7604cae1e848","tid":1800772,"uid":71063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"xavi?"},{"pid":"b364c09179b003010f41c9cc4954eeae4e19b42f","tid":1800772,"uid":318684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc0c6ff20f724b4bc9fb30cf99414be2e8a24fa8","tid":1800772,"uid":34293,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"2019利記"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:54:54.000Z","msg":"唔識英文都要識數字掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d73270048bb5501cbdcf6941b1130f01623ce1","tid":1800772,"uid":318684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e8a1b3f26fce57341071088b72d7604cae1e848","tid":1800772,"uid":71063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T06:53:34.000Z","